 ${e:\/\/Field\/history_2}<br>\nRound Times 2: ${e:\/\/Field\/roundTimes_2}<br>\nPayment 2: ${e:\/\/Field\/payment_2}<br>\n<br>\nHistory 3: ${e:\/\/Field\/history_3}<br>\nRound Times 3: ${e:\/\/Field\/roundTimes_3}<br>\nPayment 3: ${e:\/\/Field\/payment_3}<br>\n<br>\nHistory 4: ${e:\/\/Field\/history_4}<br>\nRound Times 4: ${e:\/\/Field\/roundTimes_4}<br>\nPayment 4: ${e:\/\/Field\/payment_4}<br>\n<br>\nHistory 5: ${e:\/\/Field\/history_5}<br>\nRound Times 5: ${e:\/\/Field\/roundTimes_5}<br>\nPayment 5: ${e:\/\/Field\/payment_5}<br>\n<br>\nHistory 6: ${e:\/\/Field\/history_6}<br>\nRound Times 6: ${e:\/\/Field\/roundTimes_6}<br>\nPayment 6: ${e:\/\/Field\/payment_6}<br>\n<br>\nHistory 7: ${e:\/\/Field\/history_7}<br>\nRound Times 7: ${e:\/\/Field\/roundTimes_7}<br>\nPayment 7: ${e:\/\/Field\/payment_7}<br>\n<br>\nHistory 8: ${e:\/\/Field\/history_8}<br>\nRound Times 8: ${e:\/\/Field\/roundTimes_8}<br>\nPayment 8: ${e:\/\/Field\/payment_8}<br><br>\nHistory 9: ${e:\/\/Field\/history_9}<br>\nRound Times 9: ${e:\/\/Field\/roundTimes_9}<br>\nPayment 9: ${e:\/\/Field\/payment_9}<br>\n<br>\nHistory 10: ${e:\/\/Field\/history_10}<br>\nRound Times 10: ${e:\/\/Field\/roundTimes_10}<br>\nPayment 10: ${e:\/\/Field\/payment_10}<br>\n<br>\nHistory 11: ${e:\/\/Field\/history_11}<br>\nRound Times 11: ${e:\/\/Field\/roundTimes_11}<br>\nPayment 11: ${e:\/\/Field\/payment_11}<br>\n<br>\nHistory 12: ${e:\/\/Field\/history_12}<br>\nRound Times 12: ${e:\/\/Field\/roundTimes_12}<br>\nPayment 12: ${e:\/\/Field\/payment_12}","DataExportTag":"Q11","QuestionID":"QID1218862983"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_0HtmaLNlwWAwekm","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1218862984","SecondaryAttribute":"Variations of Game Game${e:\/\/Field\/currentSymbol} In the next ${e:\/\/Field\/nBeliefElicitations}\u00a0de..","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<style>\n        .show-details-btn {\n            border: none;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            margin: 10px 0;\n        }\n        \n        .show-details-btn:hover {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n        }\n        \n        .details-content {\n            display: none;\n        }\n        \n        .details-content.show {\n            display: block;\n        }\n    <\/style>\n<div style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong>Variations of Game <\/strong><\/span>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong><span class=\"miniGame\"><span class=\"label\">Game<\/span><span class=\"sym\">${e:\/\/Field\/currentSymbol}<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<br>\n<br>\nIn the next ${e:\/\/Field\/nBeliefElicitations}&nbsp;decision screens, you will continue to play the game that you have played in the previous ${e:\/\/Field\/nRounds} rounds. <b>You will continue to play with the same two other players, ${e:\/\/Field\/playerName1} and ${e:\/\/Field\/playerName2}, who choose in the same way as before.<\/b><br>\n<br>\nAs at the end of the previous games, on the next ${e:\/\/Field\/nBeliefElicitations} decision screens, you will make different types of decisions. Instead of pressing your button, you will sometimes decide whether to press another player's button. Instead of having your bonus determined by <b>${e:\/\/Field\/playerName2}'s<\/b> choice, you may be paid according to <b>${e:\/\/Field\/playerName1}<\/b>'s choice.<br>\n<br>\nEach time, you will report your beliefs about whether and how pressing a button affects another player's choice.<br>\n<br>\nRecall: it is in your best interest to answer truthfully.    <button onclick=\"document.getElementById('detailsContent').style.display='block'; this.style.display='none';\" style=\"display: ${e:\/\/Field\/gameCounter == 1 ? 'none' : 'block'};\">Show details<\/button>\n\n<div id=\"detailsContent\" class=\"details-content\">\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"width: 80%;\" src=\"https:\/\/uzhwwf.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_6M64bgao94XKmd8\"><\/div>\n<br>\nYou will select one of multiple lines to report your beliefs. You will receive ${e:\/\/Field\/currency}${e:\/\/Field\/beliefPaymentMax} if you selected the line that corresponds to the truth. For each line by which your estimate differs from the truth, we will deduct ${e:\/\/Field\/currency}${e:\/\/Field\/beliefPaymentIncentive}.<br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;<\/div>\n<div>\nThe specific rules will be shown on each screen. Please read them carefully before making your choice.<br>\n&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:bold;\">\n\tThese are <u>not<\/u> new games. <br> The questions are all about the game you have played in the previous ${e:\/\/Field\/nRounds} rounds, and about the way in which  ${e:\/\/Field\/playerName2} and ${e:\/\/Field\/playerName1} would usually choose. <br>\n&nbsp;\n<\/div>","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n\tthis.hidePreviousButton();\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function()\n{\n    var gameCounter = \"${e:\/\/Field\/gameCounter}\";\n    \n    if (gameCounter == \"1\") {\n        document.getElementById('detailsContent').style.display = 'block';\n        document.querySelector('button').style.display = 'none';\n    }\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnUnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is unloaded*\/\n\n});","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Variations of Game Game${e:\/\/Field\/currentSymbol} In the next ${e:\/\/Field\/nBeliefElicitations}\u00a0de...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<style>\n        .show-details-btn {\n            border: none;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            font-size: 