these instructions, please select all correct statements (and only those).<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">If I'm playing with Ann and Bob and I see Ann's choice before Bob's, this means that Ann decided before Bob<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Not Selected<\/span> ","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID1218792318\/SelectableChoice\/1","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"NotSelected","QuestionID":"QID1218792318","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID1218792318","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","Type":"Expression"},"4":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID1218792318\/SelectableChoice\/3","Conjuction":"And","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">And<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Comprehension check\n\n\nTo make sure you have understood these instructions, please select all correct statements (and only those).<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Whether I press my button or not does &lt;u&gt;not&lt;\/u&gt; affect my payment<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Not Selected<\/span> ","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID1218792318\/SelectableChoice\/3","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"NotSelected","QuestionID":"QID1218792318","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID1218792318","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","Type":"Expression"},"5":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID1218792318\/SelectableChoice\/4","Conjuction":"And","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">And<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Comprehension check\n\n\nTo make sure you have understood these instructions, please select all correct statements (and only those).<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">My overall payment will be the sum of all the payments I collect over the various games and rounds of each game I play.<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Not Selected<\/span> ","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID1218792318\/SelectableChoice\/4","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"NotSelected","QuestionID":"QID1218792318","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID1218792318","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","Type":"Expression"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression"},"Message":{"description":"comprehension","libraryID":"UR_3aR5mUbLuJDsnRk","messageID":"MS_elN0gPvjo0NU2Ds","subMessageID":"VE_CUSTOM_VALIDATION_1"}}}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":7,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID165"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_0HtmaLNlwWAwekm","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID166","SecondaryAttribute":"The first three games work like this:\u00a0 You start each game with a base payment of $...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"The first three games <span id=\"clickableWord\">work<\/span> like this:&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\nYou start each game with a base payment of $${e:\/\/Field\/basePay}, which you will receive in addition to the regular Prolific payment. <u>You will receive a bonus of $${e:\/\/Field\/win} if player 2 presses their button<\/u> in the round selected to determine your payment. <u>Pressing your own button costs $${e:\/\/Field\/actionCost}<\/u>. If you pressed your button in the round selected for payment, this will be deducted from your base payment.<br>\n<br>\nYou move first. Your choice affects player 1\u2019s choice: he or she is more likely to press his or her button if you press yours.&nbsp;To confirm you are following this, click the word \"work\" at the top of this page. If you do not, the survey will terminate.<br>\n<br>\nEach game will be one of two versions; we won't tell you which one.<br>\n<br>\n<span id=\"gameDesc\">[Game description]<\/span>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"The first three games work like this:\u00a0 You start each game with a base payment of $...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":6,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page loads*\/\n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is fully displayed*\/\n\n\tlet attentionCheck = parseInt(\"attentionCheck\");\n\t\n    \/\/ Get the clickable element\n    var clickableWord = document.getElementById('clickableWord');\n\n    \/\/ Set up the click function\n    clickableWord.onclick = function() {\n        this.style.color = 'purple'; \/\/ Change the color to purple on click\n\t\tthis.style.textDecoration = 'underline';\n        Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('attentionCheck', 1); \/\/ Set the embedded data value\n    };\n\t\n\t\n\n\n  var counter     =  0;\n\n  var versions = [\n    {\n      html: \"<ul><li>Version&nbsp;1: <u>Player 2's choice affects Player 1's.<\/u> Player 1 moves after Player 2, and is more likely to press their button if Player 2 pressed theirs.<\/li><li>Version 2: <u>Player 1's choice affects Player 2's.<\/u> Player 2 moves after Player 1, and is more likely to press their button if Player 1 pressed theirs.<\/li><\/ul>\",\n      key : \"dag1first\"\n    },\n    {\n      html: \"<ul><li>Version 1: <u>Player 1's choice affects Player 2's.<\/u> Player 2 moves after Player 1, and is more likely to press their button if Player 1 pressed theirs.<\/li><li>Version 2: <u>Player 2's choice affect Player 1's.<\/u> Player 1 moves after Player 2, and is more likely to press their button if Player 2 pressed theirs.<\/li><\/ul>\",\n      key : \"dag7first\"\n    }\n  ];\n\n  var idx  = Math.random() < 0.5 ? 0 : 1;\n  var html = versions[idx].html;\n\n  jQuery(this.questionContainer).find(\"#gameDesc\").html(html);\n\n  var fieldName = \"gameVersionsDescriptionOrder\" + counter;\n  Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData(fieldName, versions[idx].key);\n\t\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnUnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is unloaded*\/\n\n});","QuestionText_Unsafe":"The first three games <span id=\"clickableWord\">work<\/span> like this:&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\nYou start each game with a base payment of $${e:\/\/Field\/basePay}, which you will receive in addition to the regular Prolific payment. <u>You will receive a bonus of $${e:\/\/Field\/win} if player 2 presses their button<\/u> in the round selected to determine your payment. <u>Pressing your own button costs $${e:\/\/Field\/actionCost}<\/u>. If you pressed your button in the round selected for payment, this will be deducted from your base payment.<br>\n<br>\nYou move first. Your choice affects player 1\u2019s choice: he or she is more likely to press his or her button if you press yours.&nbsp;To confirm you are following this, click the word \"work\" at the top of this page. If you do not, the survey will terminate.<br>\n<br>\nEach game will be one of two versions; we won't tell you which one.<br>\n<br>\n<span id=\"gameDesc\">[Game description]<\/span>","DataExportTag":"Q166","QuestionID":"QID166"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_0HtmaLNlwWAwekm","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID167","SecondaryAttribute":"Timing","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Timing","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"Timing","Selector":"PageTimer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","MinSeconds":"0","MaxSeconds":"0"},"QuestionDescription":"Timing","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"First Click"},"2":{"Display":"Last Click"},"3":{"Display":"Page Submit"},"4":{"Display":"Click Count"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":20,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Timing","DataExportTag":"Q167","QuestionID":"QID167"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_0HtmaLNlwWAwekm","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID168","SecondaryAttribute":"You will now play a different type of game","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color:#c0392b;\"><span style=\"font-size:37px;\">You will now play<\/span><\/span><\/h1>\n\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><br \/>\n<span style=\"color:#c0392b;\"><span style=\"font-size:64px;\">a different type of game<\/span><\/span><\/h1>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"You will now play a different type of game","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionJS":false,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<h1 id=\"gameTitle\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>[Game Title]<\/b><\/h1>\n<br \/>\n<span id=\"gameDesc\">[Game description]<\/span>\n<br>\n<h2>Payments<\/h2>\n<br>\nYou begin each round with a base payment of $${e:\/\/Field\/basePay}.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nIn each game, each player has a button they can press. Your payment will depend on who presses their button. Specifically:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nPlayer 2 determines whether you get a bonus. If Player 2 presses his button, you get an additional bonus of $${e:\/\/Field\/bonus}. If he does not press his button, you do not get the bonus.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nGenerally, pressing your button will cost $${e:\/\/Field\/actionCost}. Player 1 can make it free for you by pressing her button. That is, if Player 1 presses her button you can press yours for free, but if she does not, then pressing your button costs $${e:\/\/Field\/actionCost}.<br \/>\n&nbsp;","DataExportTag":"Q168","QuestionID":"QID168"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_0HtmaLNlwWAwekm","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID169","SecondaryAttribute":"Order of play You always move first. There are two versions of the game. They differ in whether t...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<h2><b>Order of play<\/b><\/h2>\n<br>\n<b>You always move first.<\/b> \n\nThere are two versions of the game. They differ in whether the Bonus Player moves before or after the Co-Player. \n<span id=\"gameDesc\">[Game description]<\/span><br>\n\n\nIn either version, your choice will definitely affect the Co-Player: <b>The Co-Player will more likely press their button if you press yours.<\/b> \n\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>We will not tell you which version you are playing; you might be playing either.<\/b> At the start of each of the ${e:\/\/Field\/nSupergames} games, the computer selects the version you will play. That version remains fixed for all ${e:\/\/Field\/nRounds} rounds of that game. Each new game may use the same or a different version.","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Order of play You always move first. There are two versions of the game. They differ in whether t...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page loads*\/\n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function()\n{\n  var versions = [\n    {\n      html: \"<ul><li>Version 1: <u>Co-Player moves before Bonus Player. <\/u> In this version, the Bonus Player may react to the Co-Player. (The order of moves is: 1. You, 2. Co-Player, 3. Bonus Player.)<\/li><li>Version 2: <u>The Bonus Player moves before the Co-Player. <\/u>In this version, the Bonus Player cannot react to the Co-Player. (The order of moves is: 1. You, 2. Bonus Player, 3. Co-Player)<\/li><\/ul>\",\n      key : 1\n    },\n    {\n      html: \"<ul><li>Version 1: <u>Bonus Player moves before Co-Player. <\/u> In this version, the Bonus Player cannot react to the Co-Player. (The order of moves is: 1. You, 2. Bonus Player, 3. Co-Player)<\/li><li>Version 2: <u>Co-Player moves before Bonus Player. <\/u> In this version, the Bonus Player may react to the Co-Player. (The order of moves is: 1. You, 2. Co-Player, 3. Bonus Player.)<\/li><\/ul>\",\n      key : 2\n    }\n  ];\n\n  var idx  = Math.random() < 0.5 ? 0 : 1;\n  var html = versions[idx].html;\n\n  jQuery(this.questionContainer).find(\"#gameDesc\").html(html);\n\n\n  var gameCounter = parseInt(\"${e:\/\/Field\/gameCounter}\");\n\n  Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData(\"gameVersionsDescriptionOrderDieter1\", versions[idx].key);\n  Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData(\"gameVersionsDescriptionOrderDieter2\", 3-versions[idx].key);\n  Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData(\"gameDescriptionDieter\", html);\n  var dieterFirst = parseInt(\"${e:\/\/Field\/dieterFirst}\");\n     if (dieterFirst == 0){\n\t  jQuery(this.questionContainer).find(\"#D2\").html(\"Unlike in the first ${e:\/\/Field\/nMigraines} games, \");\n\t  \n  }\n\t\n\tthis.hideNextButton();\n\n    var delay = parseInt(\"${e:\/\/Field\/instructionDelay}\") * 1000;\n\n    function showNextButton() {\n        jQuery(\"#NextButton\").fadeIn(1000);\n    }\n\n    \/\/ Initial delayed reveal\n    setTimeout(showNextButton, delay);\n\n    \/\/ Ensure it stays visible if the tab is switched or re-rendered\n    document.addEventListener(\"visibilitychange\", function() {\n        if (!document.hidden) {\n            showNextButton();\n        }\n    });\n\n    \/\/ Also re-show it when the window regains focus\n    window.addEventListener(\"focus\", function() {\n        showNextButton();\n    });\n\n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnUnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is unloaded*\/\n\n});","QuestionText_Unsafe":"<h2><b>Order of play<\/b><\/h2>\n<br \/>\nThere are two versions of this game that differ in who plays when. We will not tell you which version you are playing; you might be playing either. In both versions, Player 1 plays before you. The versions differ by whether Player 2 moves first or last.<br \/>\n<span id=\"gameDesc\">[Game description]<\/span>\nThe version is determined at the beginning of each of the four games and stays the same for all ${e:\/\/Field\/nRounds} rounds of each game.","DataExportTag":"Q169","QuestionID":"QID169"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_0HtmaLNlwWAwekm","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID170","SecondaryAttribute":"What you will see In each round, you will make a choice before observing any other player\u2019s choic.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<h2><b>What you will see<\/b><\/h2>\n<br>\nIn each round, you will make a choice before observing any other player&rsquo;s choice.&nbsp;After that, you will then see the computer players' choices.\n<br><br>\n\nYou can make your choices using either your mouse or your keyboard. If you're using your keyboard, press <em>Y<\/em> for \"Yes\" and <em>N<\/em> for \"No\".\n\n<br><br>\nThe <b>order in which the computer players' choices are revealed<\/b> is determined at the start of each game and remains fixed throughout that game:\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>In some games, you will first see the <b>Co-Player&rsquo;s<\/b> choice, then the <b>Bonus Player&rsquo;s<\/b> choice.<\/li>\n\t<li>In other games, you will first see the <b>Bonus Player&rsquo;s<\/b> choice, then the <b>Co-Player&rsquo;s<\/b> choice.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<b>The order in which you see their choices<\/b> does not indicate the version of the game you are playing. It <b>does not reflect who actually moves first or last.<\/b>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"What you will see In each round, you will make a choice before observing any other player\u2019s choic...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":9,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<h2><b>What you will see<\/b><\/h2>\n<br \/>\nEach round proceeds like this:\n<ol>\n\t<li>You observe whether pressing your button is free or costs $${e:\/\/Field\/aCost}, as determined by <b>player 1<\/b>&rsquo;s choice.<\/li>\n\t<li>You choose whether or not to press your button.<\/li>\n\t<li>You observe <b>player 2<\/b>&#39;s choice<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<br \/>\n<b>Important: <\/b>You will always observe Player 2&rsquo;s choice last, regardless of whether player 2 actually moved first or last.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nYou will make your choices in a decision screen like this:<br \/>\n<br \/>\n[Screenshot]","DataExportTag":"Q170","QuestionID":"QID170","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page loads*\/\n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function()\n{\n\tthis.hideNextButton();\n\n    var delay = parseInt(\"${e:\/\/Field\/instructionDelay}\") * 1000;\n\n    function showNextButton() {\n        jQuery(\"#NextButton\").fadeIn(1000);\n    }\n\n    \/\/ Initial delayed reveal\n    setTimeout(showNextButton, delay);\n\n    \/\/ Ensure it stays visible if the tab is switched or re-rendered\n    document.addEventListener(\"visibilitychange\", function() {\n        if (!document.hidden) {\n            showNextButton();\n        }\n    });\n\n    \/\/ Also re-show it when the window regains focus\n    window.addEventListener(\"focus\", function() {\n        showNextButton();\n    });\n\n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnUnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is unloaded*\/\n\n});","DisplayLogic":{"0":{"0":{"Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">treatment<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> endog <\/span>","LeftOperand":"treatment","LogicType":"EmbeddedField","Operator":"EqualTo","RightOperand":"endog","Type":"Expression"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression","inPage":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_0HtmaLNlwWAwekm","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID171","SecondaryAttribute":"Comprehension check To make sure you have understood these instructions, please select all correc...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Comprehension check<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br \/>\nTo make sure you have understood these instructions, please select all correct statements (and only those).<\/div>","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n    \/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page loads*\/\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function()\n{\n    var that = this;\n    var correctAnswer = \"2,4,6,7\";  \/\/ Change this to your correct answer\n    var wrongCount = Number(Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.getEmbeddedData(\"wrongCountDieter\")) || 0;\n    var allAnswers = Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.getEmbeddedData(\"allAnswersDieter\") || \"\";\n    \n    var nextBtn = document.getElementById(\"NextButton\");\n    nextBtn.addEventListener(\"click\", function(e)\n    {\n        var userAnswer = that.getSelectedChoices() || \"none\";\n        \n        \/\/ Add this answer to history\n        if (allAnswers === \"\") {\n            allAnswers = userAnswer;\n        } else {\n            allAnswers = allAnswers + \"||\" + userAnswer;\n        }\n        \n        \/\/ Check if correct\n        if (userAnswer === correctAnswer) {\n            \/\/ Correct!\n        } else {\n            \/\/ Wrong\n            wrongCount++;\n        }\n        \n        \/\/ Save data\n        Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData(\"wrongCountDieter\", wrongCount);\n        Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData(\"allAnswersDieter\", allAnswers);\n        \n    }, true);\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnUnload(function()\n{\n    \/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is unloaded*\/\n});","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"MACOL","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","NumColumns":2},"QuestionDescription":"Comprehension check To make sure you have understood these instructions, please select all correc...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"If I'm playing with Ann and Bob and I see Bob's choice after Ann\u2019s, this means that Bob decided after Ann."},"2":{"Display":"If I'm playing with Ann and Bob and I see Bob's choice after Ann\u2019s, this does <u>not<\/u> mean that Bob decided after Ann."},"3":{"Display":"Whether I press my button or not does <u>not<\/u> affect my payment."},"4":{"Display":"My overall payment will be determined by one decision randomly selected from throughout the study."},"5":{"Display":"My overall payment will be the sum of all the payments I collect over the various games and rounds of each game I play."},"6":{"Display":"Pressing my button will always cost ${e:\/\/Field\/currency}${e:\/\/Field\/aCost}."},"7":{"Display":"There are two versions of the game. The version will be determined in the beginning of each game, and will stay in place for all ${e:\/\/Field\/nRounds} rounds."}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2,3,4,5,6,7],"Randomization":{"Advanced":null,"TotalRandSubset":"","Type":"All"},"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"CustomValidation","MinChoices":"1","CustomValidation":{"Logic":{"0":{"0":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID171\/SelectableChoice\/1","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Comprehension check To make sure you have understood these instructions, please select all correc...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">If I'm playing with Ann and Bob and I see Bob's choice after Ann\u2019s, this means that Bob decided after Ann.<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Not Selected<\/span> ","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID171\/SelectableChoice\/1","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"NotSelected","QuestionID":"QID171","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID171","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","Type":"Expression"},"1":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID171\/SelectableChoice\/2","Conjuction":"And","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">And<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Comprehension check To make sure you have understood these instructions, please select all correc...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">If I'm playing with Ann and Bob and I see