=\"label\">Game<\/span>\n    <span class=\"sym\">${e:\/\/Field\/currentSymbol}<\/span>\n  <\/span>\n<\/h1>\n","DataExportTag":"Q178","QuestionID":"QID178"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_0HtmaLNlwWAwekm","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID179","SecondaryAttribute":"You will play this game with ${e:\/\/Field\/playerName2}. \u00a0 ${e:\/\/Field\/playerName2} The computer ha..","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\nYou will play this game with ${e:\/\/Field\/playerName2}. <span id=\"D2\">&nbsp;<\/span>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:300px;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"Player\" class=\"panel-icon\" src=\"${e:\/\/Field\/playerIcon2}\"><\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">${e:\/\/Field\/playerName2}<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<br>\n\t<b>The computer has now determined which version of the game you will play.<\/b>\n\t\n\t<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"You will play this game with ${e:\/\/Field\/playerName2}. \u00a0 ${e:\/\/Field\/playerName2} The computer ha...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n\tthis.hidePreviousButton();\n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function()\n{\n\tconst loopNum = \"${lm:\/\/CurrentLoopNumber}\";\n\tif (loopNum != 1){\n\t\tvar loopPrev = loopNum - 1;\n\t\tvar name1prev = Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.getEmbeddedData('playerName1_' + loopPrev);\n\t\tvar name2prev = Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.getEmbeddedData('playerName2_' + loopPrev);\n\t\tjQuery(this.questionContainer).find(\"#D2\").html(\"They may play differently than \" + name2prev 