\">And<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">order<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> AYX <\/span>","Conjuction":"And"},"Type":"If"},"1":{"0":{"LogicType":"EmbeddedField","LeftOperand":"nSupergames","Operator":"EqualTo","RightOperand":"3","Type":"Expression","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">nSupergames<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> 3 <\/span>"},"1":{"LogicType":"LoopAndMerge","LeftOperand":"BL_5njDz3P0yi3K2zk,3","RightOperand":"lm:\/\/CurrentLoop","Operator":"EqualTo","Type":"Expression","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">And<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Loop 3: ${e:\/\/Field\/mainDieter3}<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\">Current Loop<\/span>","Conjuction":"And"},"2":{"LogicType":"EmbeddedField","LeftOperand":"order","Operator":"EqualTo","RightOperand":"AYX","Type":"Expression","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">And<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">order<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> AYX <\/span>","Conjuction":"And"},"Type":"ElseIf"},"Type":"BooleanExpression","inPage":false},"ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">In this game, <b>you will always see the Bonus Player\u2019s choice before the Co-Player\u2019s choice<\/b>, regardless of who actually moved when.&nbsp;<\/div>","DataExportTag":"Q439","QuestionID":"QID439"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_0HtmaLNlwWAwekm","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID44","SecondaryAttribute":"Instructions for games 4 to 6 In this part of the study, you'll play similar games that is one of...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong>Instructions for games 4 to 6<\/strong><\/span><\/div>\n<br \/>\n<br \/>\nIn this part of the study, you&#39;ll play similar games that is one of the two versions.&nbsp;<u>The only difference is the following:<\/u>&nbsp;In some rounds, you are forced to press or not press your button. Then you observe player 1&rsquo;s choice, followed by player 2&rsquo;s choice &mdash; regardless of whether player 1 actually moved before or after player 2. In other rounds, you decide whether to press your button as before, but you do NOT observe player 1&#39;s or player 2&#39;s choice.&nbsp;<br \/>\n<br \/>\nWhen you are forced to press or not press your button, you can only select the option with your mouse. When you decide whether to press your button, you can only use your keyboard:&nbsp;Press &quot;y&quot; for Yes and &quot;n&quot; for No.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nYou will be paid for exactly one round in which you&#39;ve made your decision, selected at random at the end of the study. You receive the bonus of $${e:\/\/Field\/win} if player 2 pressed his or her button in that round. In either case, you also pay the cost of $${e:\/\/Field\/actionCost} if you pressed your button in that round.&nbsp;","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n\tthis.hidePreviousButton();\n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is fully displayed*\/\n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnUnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is unloaded*\/\n\n});","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"instructionsMainExo","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Instructions for games 4 to 6 In this part of the study, you'll play similar games that is one of...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID44"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_0HtmaLNlwWAwekm","Element":"SQ","Pri